<paragraph id="385B36BE667ADF0F75E09E2932FEF881" blockId="0.[166,1225,1577,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">
R e m a r k s. As it was indicated earlier (
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667ADF0F77849E2A33FEF9E6" author="Mikhailov, K. G. &amp; Fet, V. Ya." box="[703,957,1577,1604]" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" pagination="168 - 186" refId="ref1054" refString="Mikhailov, K. G., Fet, V. Ya. 1986. Materials to the fauna of spiders (Aranei) of Turkmenia. I. Families Anyphaenidae, Sparassidae, Zoridae, Clubionidae, Micariidae, Oxyopidae). In: Heptner, M. V., ed. Fauna, sistematika i filogeniya bespozvonochnykh zhivotnykh. Sbornik trudov Zoologicheskogo muzeya MGU, 24, 168 - 186 [In Russian]." type="journal article" year="1986">Mikhailov, Fet, 1986</bibRefCitation>
), the types of 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667ADF0F71579E293144F9C1" authorityName="Mikhailov" authorityYear="2015" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="modesta">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F71579E293144F9C1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">Micaria modesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are deposited in the Zoological Museum of the 
<collectingRegion id="FA20F85C667ADF0F767E9E4933A9F9C1" box="[837,1002,1609,1636]" country="Russia" name="Moscow" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">Moscow State</collectingRegion>
University, 
<collectingCountry id="40F3762E667ADF0F71469E4A348AF9C1" box="[1149,1225,1609,1635]" name="Russia" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">Russia</collectingCountry>
(ZMMU), together with other spider species described and identified by A. I. Kroneberg from the A. P. Fedchenko Turkestan Expedition (
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667ADF0F77C79E8A338AF906" author="Kroneberg, A. I." box="[764,969,1673,1700]" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" pagination="1 - 55" refId="ref922" refString="Kroneberg, A. I. 1875. A. P. Fedchenko. Voyage in Turkestan. Spiders. Araneae, Izvestiya Obshchestva lyubitelei estestvoznaniya, antropologii i etnografii. 19 (3), I - IV + 1 - 55 + 5 plates [In Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1875">Kroneberg, 1875</bibRefCitation>
). The examination of these 
<typeStatus id="E75F881C667ADF0F75D09EA93113F966" box="[235,336,1706,1732]" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">syntypes</typeStatus>
confirms the identity of 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667ADF0F77479EA9336CF961" authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1875" box="[636,815,1706,1731]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rossica">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F77479EA9336CF961" box="[636,815,1706,1731]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">Micaria rossica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667ADF0F764E9EA933BCF961" authorityName="Mikhailov" authorityYear="2015" box="[885,1023,1705,1732]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="modesta">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F764E9EA933CCF961" box="[885,911,1706,1731]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F76A59EAA33BCF961" box="[926,1023,1705,1731]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">modesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Both names are given in 1875, but the former one is regularly used as valid in taxonomic and numerous faunistic publications, whereas the latter one is known only from catalogues and synonymy lists. So, the name 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667ADF0F74449F0931B7F881" authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1875" box="[383,500,1802,1828]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="567" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rossica">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F74449F0931DAF881" box="[383,409,1802,1827]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667ADF0F749D9F0931B7F881" box="[422,500,1802,1827]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">rossica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is to be retained.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="385B36BE667BDF0E75D898B3311CFEE8" blockId="1.[174,1232,175,330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">
Due to the wide Holarctic range and the morphological variability of its genitalia, 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667BDF0E759598D33127FF4B" authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1875" box="[174,356,208,233]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rossica">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E759598D33127FF4B" box="[174,356,208,233]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">Micaria rossica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[compare the figs in 
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667BDF0E774C98CC331DFF48" author="Wunderlich, J." box="[631,862,207,234]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="233 - 340" refId="ref1295" refString="Wunderlich, J. 1980. Revision der europaischen Arten der Gattung Micaria Westring 1851, mit Anmerkungen zu den ubrigen palaarktischen Arten (Arachnida: Araneida: Gnaphosidae). Zoologische Beitrage, Neue Folge, (1979), 25 (2), 233 - 340." type="journal article" year="1980">Wunderlich (1980)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667BDF0E769998CC348AFF48" author="Mikhailov, K. G. &amp; Fet, V. Ya." box="[930,1225,207,234]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="168 - 186" refId="ref1054" refString="Mikhailov, K. G., Fet, V. Ya. 1986. Materials to the fauna of spiders (Aranei) of Turkmenia. I. Families Anyphaenidae, Sparassidae, Zoridae, Clubionidae, Micariidae, Oxyopidae). In: Heptner, M. V., ed. Fauna, sistematika i filogeniya bespozvonochnykh zhivotnykh. Sbornik trudov Zoologicheskogo muzeya MGU, 24, 168 - 186 [In Russian]." type="journal article" year="1986">Mikhailov &amp; Fet (1986)</bibRefCitation>
] was known under different names, like 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667BDF0E77BE98F333DCFEAB" authority="Simon, 1878" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1878" box="[645,927,239,266]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scenica">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E77BE98F332DCFEAB" box="[645,671,240,265]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E779598F33343FEAB" box="[686,768,240,265]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">scenica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667BDF0E763298EC33DCFEAB" author="Simon, E." box="[777,927,239,265]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="1 - 334" refId="ref1215" refString="Simon, E. 1878. Les arachnides de France. Paris, 4, 1 - 334 + pl. XIV - XVI." type="journal article" year="1878">Simon, 1878</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667BDF0E769798F330ABFE88" authority="Charitonov, 1951" authorityName="Charitonov" authorityYear="1951" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hissarica">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E769798F33385FEAB" box="[940,966,240,265]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E76EF98EC347AFEAB" box="[980,1081,239,265]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">hissarica</emphasis>
Charitonov, 1951
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="FFE44D3D667BDF0E75CF99133208FE88" authority="Charitonov, 1951" authorityName="Charitonov" authorityYear="1951" box="[244,587,271,298]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Micaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zhadini">
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E75CF9913314DFE8B" box="[244,270,272,297]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="0A90EAAC667BDF0E7427990C3137FE8B" box="[284,372,271,297]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">zhadini</emphasis>
Charitonov, 1951
</taxonomicName>
, which have been already synonymized (
<bibRefCitation id="5C754B4F667BDF0E7116990C3110FEE8" author="World Spider Catalog" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" refId="ref1261" refString="World Spider Catalog. 2015. World Spider Catalog. Natural History Museum Bern. online at http: // wsc. nmbe. ch, version 16.5, accessed on 15.09. 2015" type="url" year="2015">World Spider Catalog, 2015</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
